column3: Time to get back to work! Heres your cash.
Take your cut and get outta here kid.
I hope you don't expect me to pay full price for that?
Ca-Ching! Heres your change. Did you want a receipt?
I don't remember ordering anything, meh, take my money anyway!
I can't afford to pay, do you want to come in?_NEWLINE_No?_NEWLINE_All right, heres your money.
Thanks Dearie, good to see kids these days still earn their pocket money and aren't playing all day, when I was a kid...
Dear Sir/Madam, your delivery was greatly appreciated. Sincerly, The Businessman.
